## Educational/Science Illustration

### Tea Compounds Diagram

**Prompt:**
```
Scientific illustration, molecular structure of tea tannins and catechins interacting with meat protein fibers, clean infographic style, blue and green color scheme, educational diagram, labeled components, white background, medical illustration aesthetic, clear and informative --ar 3:2 --v 6
```

### Tea Type Comparison Chart

**Prompt:**
```
Infographic design, comparison of different tea types for meat marinades: black tea, pu-erh, oolong, green tea, jasmine tea, each with small tea leaf illustration, tannin level bars, best meat pairing icons, clean modern design, muted earth tones, editorial infographic --ar 16:9 --v 6
```

